sub_title: Director of translation agency "Rusland Vertaal- en Adviesbureau"
summary:
Graduated as translator Russian (Higher Professional Education) and cultural anthropologist (university). Working as sworn translator Russian <=> Dutch, Russian language teacher, subtitler and constructor of Russian language exams. Working experience in this field since 1999.

Three times prizewinner of literature translation contests
Recommended sworn translator of the Russian Consulate in The Hague

Specialities: Official documents, legal documents, culture and entertainment, subtitling, social sciences, literature, agriculture, communication.
